## 五、部署与运行

### 5.1 开发环境

```bash
# 1. 克隆插件仓库
git clone https://github.com/your-org/zhiguan-openclaw-plugin.git
cd zhiguan-openclaw-plugin

# 2. 安装依赖
npm install

# 3. 链接到OpenClaw扩展目录
openclaw plugins install -l ./

# 4. 配置OpenClaw
# 编辑 ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json，添加上述插件配置

# 5. 重启Gateway
openclaw gateway restart

# 6. 验证插件加载
openclaw plugins list
# 应该看到: zhiguan (止观AI)

# 7. 测试工具
openclaw tools list
# 应该看到: zhiguan_start_practice, zhiguan_end_practice, zhiguan_get_stats
```

### 5.2 生产环境

```bash
# 1. 构建插件
npm run build

# 2. 打包发布
npm pack

# 3. 安装到生产环境
openclaw plugins install ./zhiguan-openclaw-plugin-1.0.0.tgz

# 4. 配置生产数据库（PostgreSQL）
# 修改 openclaw.json:
# "database": { "type": "postgres", "connection": "postgresql://..." }

# 5. 启动服务
openclaw gateway start
```

